title: New Star de Douala
text: New Star FC is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club in <a href="Cameroon">Cameroon</a>, Douala. They play in <a href="Elite%20One">Elite One</a> - the top-flight football league of Cameroon. <a href="Stade%20de%20la%20R%C3%A9unification">Stade de la Réunification</a>, which has a capacity of 30,000, is their home venue. They played in the <a href="2016%20CAF%20Confederation%20Cup">2016 CAF Confederation Cup</a>.
